<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Ceritanya Kopi</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,600;1,400&family=Lato:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    :root {
      --coklat-tua: #3b2314;
      --coklat-medium: #6b3f24;
      --coklat-muda: #a0693a;
      --krem: #f5efe6;
      --hijau-gelap: #4a5c3e;
      --putih: #ffffff;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
      background-color: var(--putih);
      color: var(--coklat-tua);
    }

    .navbar {
      background-color: var(--putih);
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e8ddd0;
      padding: 12px 40px;
    }

    .navbar-brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .logo-circle {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      background-color: var(--coklat-tua);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-direction: column;
      line-height: 1.2;
      padding: 4px;
    }

    .logo-circle span:first-child {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      color: var(--putih);
      font-size: 9px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .logo-circle span:last-child {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      color: #c9a96e;
      font-size: 8px;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .nav-center-link {
      color: var(--coklat-tua) !important;
      font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .nav-center-link:hover {
      color: var(--coklat-muda) !important;
    }

    .btn-login {
      color: var(--coklat-tua);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      padding: 6px 16px;
    }

    .btn-login:hover {
      color: var(--coklat-muda);
    }

    .btn-register {
      background-color: var(--hijau-gelap);
      color: var(--putih) !important;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 14px;
      padding: 8px 22px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }

    .btn-register:hover {
      background-color: #3a4a30;
      color: var(--putih) !important;
    }

    /* ======= HERO SECTION ======= */
    .hero-section {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      height: 420px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-image {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: center top;
      display: block;
    }

    .hero-overlay {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0.08) 0%, rgba(30,15,5,0.45) 100%);
    }

    /* ======= TAGLINE SECTION ======= */
    .tagline-section {
      background-color: var(--coklat-tua);
      padding: 56px 60px;
    }

    .tagline-quote {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 28px;
      color: var(--krem);
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.4;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .tagline-quote::before,
    .tagline-quote::after {
      content: '"';
      font-size: 32px;
      color: #c9a96e;
    }

    .tagline-content {
      display: flex;
      gap: 40px;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .tagline-img-wrap {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      width: 260px;
      height: 200px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .tagline-img-wrap img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .tagline-text {
      color: #d4c4b0;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.85;
      font-weight: 300;
      padding-top: 8px;
    }

   
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .navbar { padding: 12px 20px; }
      .hero-section { height: 260px; }
      .tagline-section { padding: 40px 24px; }
      .tagline-quote { font-size: 20px; }
      .tagline-content { flex-direction: column; }
      .tagline-img-wrap { width: 100%; height: 200px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

 
  <nav class="navbar d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between">
    <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
      <div class="logo-circle">
        <span>Ceritanya</span>
        <span>Kopi</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/menus" class="nav-center-link">Coffee Corner</a>

    <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2">
      <a href="/login" class="btn-login">Log in</a>
      <a href="/register" class="btn-register">Register</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

 
  <section class="hero-section">
    <img
      src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1445116572660-236099ec97a0?w=1400&auto=format&fit=crop&q=80"
      alt="Suasana Ceritanya Kopi"
      class="hero-image"
    >
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
  </section>

  
  <section class="tagline-section">
    <p class="tagline-quote">Tempat di Mana Cerita dan Kopi Bertemu.</p>

    <div class="tagline-content">
      <div class="tagline-img-wrap">
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1509042239860-f550ce710b93?w=600&auto=format&fit=crop&q=80"
          alt="Secangkir kopi"
        >
      </div>
      <p class="tagline-text">
        Ruang hangat untuk berbagi cerita, menikmati kebersamaan, dan menemukan ketenangan di tengah
        kesibukan. Ditemani kopi pilihan, sajian yang dibuat dengan sepenuh hati, serta suasana yang nyaman,
        setiap kunjungan di Ceritanya Kopi adalah kesempatan untuk menciptakan cerita baru yang layak dikenang.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
